        "Description": "December 23, 2008, 4:00 PM, Bratislava, Slovakia. Good afternoon 47, your targets are now guest Julian and Hotel Staff Tumar Bimbombur. You have to also retrieve the either natural or artificial christmas tree to your suite. After you eliminate all targets, phone and ask Mária Pietrová, what christmas tree would she like. Merry Christmas 47!\rSources:\rhttps://www.cas.sk/clanok/100330/sexi-celebrity-umele-ci-prirodne/",
